Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:21.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}掌上的微风 在光芒中一闪一闪地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:35.21,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}我已经能用全新的笑容 向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:47.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}尽管回忆溢满心头 我的朝气绝不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:57.27,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无所谓在干掉的泪痕中 有一扇通往梦想的门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:01:01.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}如果烦恼就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:10.03,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}没错 我会以迎接朋友的方式 温柔地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:14.79,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:23.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无意间悲伤虽然涌上心头 我也会试着与人和好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:27.80,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}因为这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#12爱情的危机!你明明说过爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.87,0:02:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4点20分,时间应该还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在干嘛 居然西装笔挺的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员跟三鹰约…约会?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两张票很贵耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本,是我啦,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空的话 要不要一起去看个电影?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我有票,指定席
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要请我看电影吗? 真是难得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别傻了,谁要请你啊 你要给我付钱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?手头紧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有女朋友的话 我就不会打电话给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么意思! 你这种仿佛在取笑我的笑声!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也没资格说我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且我可是好心邀你出来看电影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人要打电话,我挂了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是五代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.99,0:04:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我是谁吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前在同一家酒店打工的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫七尾小津江
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了,小津江
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我没什么印象吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦,因为我都在外头送货 很少在店里面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我对于人名 一向不太记得住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你把眼镜拿下来 简直变成另外一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把打工赚的钱 拿去配了一副隐形眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐形眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是打算买别的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来突然买了隐形眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜不出来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你大概也猜不出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊,这是电影票
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,指定席
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近这部电影很受女生欢迎耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么听说 才特地去买的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喔,我好想看这部电影喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你愿意的话 要不要一起去看?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 好像是我硬要你带我去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说,我也正愁没人陪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会造成你的困扰吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员和三鹰到哪里去了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,现在他们两个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?快点走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们改走另外一条路 走另外一条路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?车站就在前面耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正走就对了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你是五代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也出来约会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不能小看你 居然把手放在人家肩上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我以前打工的同事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点走吧,电影要来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个真是速配的一对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他明明跟我说他爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却有个那么年轻可爱的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是在捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过份了 竟然玩弄女人的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,不快点的话 我们的音乐会也要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,再一下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不原谅你!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在说你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恐怖…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这种电影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好没有找管理员来看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她是管理员就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(莫札特)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场音乐会好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能约你一起来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次请再跟我一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊,如果你愿意邀我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的 能和你这样在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况,今晚你真的好美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:10:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,只有今晚而已吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好坏喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然有个那么 年轻可爱的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,我们找个地方吃晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还想辩解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不像男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以喝一点酒吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要开车,所以不能喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我不会叫你喝酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天有点怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恐怖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心 看来暂时会吃不下饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然黏在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们平常都是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横滨有个夜景很美的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点远
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你方便的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,横滨可能太远了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是横滨还是哪里 我都陪你去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究…究竟是怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能问你一件事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天愿意和我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是为了想去听音乐会而已吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其它的理由是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你在一起,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,你的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一能够让我远离管理员工作 松口气的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松口气…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一个男人而言呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也有女朋友吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也?你有男朋友吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,我不是在说我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有什么男朋友!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以问你一件事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的电影 你原本是想跟谁去看?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在路上遇见的那个女人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是 她有个很登对的男朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管原本要跟谁去看 我今天真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我在一起很无聊吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啊,你很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴喔 换了隐形眼镜终于有了价值
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过这座公园可以抄近路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常我都走商店街回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有你陪着我 所以我不用害怕,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定反而会更恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑,我是开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然问这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你愿意把我当女人看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是打工的同事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能被一时的感情冲昏了头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是吻一下应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我…我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小津江…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次还能见面吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩是不是对我有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吓人好不好!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.20,0:17:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么眼神?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.87,0:17:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有做任何不轨的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有一瞬间曾经犹豫过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过结果我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么叫得这么悲伤呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么,不是管理员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员还没回来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,都已经11点半了说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,不可以逃避现实喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候喝酒最好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么跟什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要随便跑进来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是来分担你的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有什么不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过说到三鹰这个男人 手脚好像很快喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊,那个眼神很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员她不会的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,管理员对这种事 没有什么免疫力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个涉世未深的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很容易被浪漫的气氛迷住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜雾包围着我们幽会的恋情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想说 夜雾,今晚也谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要难过 痛快喝个两杯把一切都忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,已经这么晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.30,0:20:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她今晚大概会外宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔一两次早上回来也没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊,又不是小孩子的约会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来,喝吧 反正今晚她也不会回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,结果弄到这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会,不过我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以再约你出来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次不要只为了松口气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跌到谷底,坠入痛苦的深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求幸福 却坠入痛苦的深渊里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了,被甩了,被讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好借酒浇愁…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请下车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.43,0:21:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来喝一杯好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走,睡觉去,睡觉去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我!放开我!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.99,0:21:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以去,冷静一点,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我!放开我!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.33,0:22:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候不能去打扰人家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.24,0:22:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.65,0:22:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的力量真伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认输了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.69,0:22:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以,求求你,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.06,0:22:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.26,0:22:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.17,0:22:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,不可以这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.23,0:22:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.67,0:22:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的西装弄脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么嘛,真令人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.85,0:22:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得应该说无聊呢? 还是有趣呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,三更半夜的不要发出 那种会引人误会的叫声啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.15,0:22:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在期待些什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.49,0:23:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去喝酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.23,0:23:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续喝,继续喝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.10,0:23:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你也进来喝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.00,0:23:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.77,0:23:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.57,0:23:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.55,0:23:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很生气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.92,0:23:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有很多女人打电话来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.82,0:23:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且每天打,打个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.52,0:24:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回 ‘万人迷的五代?当心桃色电话!’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.49,0:24:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代竟然笑眯眯的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.13,0:24:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么嘛,那个色小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.49,0:24:04.49,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.41,0:24:35.69,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}为何你能如此若无其事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.72,0:24:43.03,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}光只是眨个眼 就能让我悸动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.06,0:24:51.62,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}使我身陷险境
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.28,0:25:06.30,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}明明已经可以相爱 偏偏时机还不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.33,0:25:18.56,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}我快要忍受不了 快要变成了愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.60,0:25:23.94,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}真是痛苦的折磨

